Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:46.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}何度息絶えそうでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}ただ真っ直ぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:53.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Don't give up the fight　Time to ignite
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:04:00.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}この身をかけて　挑む世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:07.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}いっそあるがままに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:12.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}その全てを包み込むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:29.31,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}心中的梦 早已不再只属于自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:35.73,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}掀开那 新的一页
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:39.90,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}将现实挫败 把命运主宰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:42.82,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}满腔热诚正澎湃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:46.37,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}哪怕残酷到令人窒息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.66,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}也会不离不弃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:53.58,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}莫轻易言败 卷土又重来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:04:00.63,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}尽全力冲破障碍 向世界宣战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:07.51,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我愿以原本的姿态
